The all-new Minisforum MS-S1 MAX is here with AMD’s Ryzen™ AI Max+ 395 and RDNA 3.5 graphics. We finish with thermals, noise, and real power draw from the wall to see if this tiny workstation can replace a full desktop. #MS1MAX #Minisforum #MiniPC #RyzenAIMax395 #etaprime
